title: New 2017 KTM 390 Duke vs Bajaj Dominar 400: price, features and specs - The Financial Express
text: New 2017 KTM 390 Duke vs Bajaj Dominar 400: price, features and specs New 2017 KTM 390 Duke vs Bajaj Dominar 400: price, features and specs Bajaj Dominar 400 is the first of the manufacturer's range of high-performance motorcycles, however when it was launched the KTM Duke 390 was already in the Indian market and now has received an upgrade. With similar engine capacity, the 390 Duke is more powerful than the Dominar 400, but Bajaj's latest offering has price on its side. Following is a comparison of the two based on various aspects.
